Notes

The line above is exactly 80 chars wide including borders.
Each line’s interior is split into Left (26) | Center (26) | Right (26).
Top line content:
Left: ISAAC version + Session ID
Center: System state (e.g., READY/RUNNING/ERROR)
Right: Cloud, AI, VPN status



